An Investigation on $\mathbb{Z}/n\mathbb{Z}$ $\mathbb{Z}/n\mathbb{Z}$ is the set of all congruence classes of the integers for a modulus $n$. It can be written as $\mathbb{Z}_n$, $\mathbb{Z}/n$ or $\mathbb{Z}/n\mathbb{Z}$. Finished Xiaozhe Yao 2019-11-12 10:17 AM
